re on July 3, adding a speech beneath the granite faces of four consequential presidents to his schedule of events surrounding the 250th anniversary of the nation's founding.\r\n\r\nA White House official told USA TODAY that Trump would be heading to South Dakota for the event at the national memorial that's hosted by Freedom 250, the group working with the administration to put on anniversary events.\r\n\r\nThe celebration will include fireworks, military bands, flyovers, tributes to the Armed Services, and a speech by the president that the organization said would commemorate the nation's 250th anniversary and chart a course for America's next chapter.\"\r\n\r\nA lottery was held in april for public tickets. Lottery is finished, no public tickets available.   :( \r\n\r\n", "author": "phibetared", "created": 1782484994125, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "FreedomLubber", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Trump at Mount Rushmore - JULY 3rd  (too late for tickets though)", "last_comment_created": 1782485459408, "content": "<p>From USA Today:</p>\n<p>&quot;President Donald Trump will headline a pre-Independence Day celebration at Mount Rushmore on July 3, adding a speech beneath the granite faces of four consequential presidents to his schedule of events surrounding the 250th anniversary of the nation's founding.</p>\n<p>A White House official told USA TODAY that Trump would be heading to South Dakota for the event at the national memorial that's hosted by Freedom 250, the group working with the administration to put on anniversary events.</p>\n<p>The celebration will include fireworks, military bands, flyovers, tributes to the Armed Services, and a speech by the president that the organization said would commemorate the nation's 250th anniversary and chart a course for America's next chapter.&quot;</p>\n<p>A lottery was held in april for public tickets. Lottery is finished, no public tickets available.   :(</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 1, "score_up": 28, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASt1O89kG", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 21, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8699778, "raw_content": "", "author": "VanillaCupCake", "created": 1782490441499, "profile_picture": "skHhaQnk6Zfk", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "VanillaCupCake", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.scored.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASt1O89kG.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.scored.co/post/E8Setyv6U3sf.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/4Ce7egNJOlvjIrxr.jpeg", "width": 549, "content-type": "jpeg", "height": 653}], "blurhash": "UJJ%??0101E2~pIAs9t6tSD%ofxa-:RPoft7", "full_resolution": [653, 549]}, "title": "TURN TO THE LORD.... REBUKE SAMYAZA...ACCEPT JESUS AS YOUR SAVIOR!", "last_comment_created": 1782490715060, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 2, "score_up": 21, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_com